                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: net/mlx5: Always stop health timer during driver removal (CVE-2024-40906)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: net/mlx5e: SHAMPO, Fix invalid WQ linked list unlink (CVE-2024-44970)&lt;/li&gt;
